Interface LifecycleState

public interface LifecycleState
extends DimensionsObject

Represents a Dimensions lifecycle state.

getAutoBuild

boolean getAutoBuild()
                     throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Returns whether to perform a build as soon as a change occurs that causes a build area update. If a build stage is not assigned to this lifecycle state, then this method will always return false.

true/false
